Package: robsentiment
Title: Performs Basic Text cleaning and Sentiment Analysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Robert", "Levine", email = "levine1@usf.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: rob_text cleans your text by making all the characters lowercase, removing numbers, removing multiple spaces, and removing punctuation. rob_sentiment_scores returns a value from -5 to 5 indicating the sentiment of your text. rob_stopwords removes stopwords from text. rob_token tokenizes your text and rob_cloud creates a wordcloud that differentiates the postive and negative words.
License: GPL-3
Imports:
    tidytext,
    tm,
    wordcloud,
    RColorBrewer
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3.9000
